It's Game Theory...THE GAME! Super Theorist JFinnGames made the first ever Game Theory game featuring all your favorite theorists doing what we all do best...theorizing? Wait, what WOULD I do in a video game? ...Only one way to find out! 

JFinnGames this game is awesome! Thank you for making it and we hope you continue with the game. We would love to play it more.

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive
